{"tid":2499655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8天7夜史上最長！漢光軍演首次假定共軍若犯台 防衛作戰可「撐過一周」","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T07:24:51.000Z","uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eed9ae164643f5642065e0291b7f7f70e2b420ea","tid":2499655,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210419/RF25IRRNTZAXXLNPHEZZWMUCME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210419%2FRF25IRRNTZAXXLNPHEZZWMUCME%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=9f6c932d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210419%2FRF25IRRNTZAXXLNPHEZZWMUCME%2F&h=8397415a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210419/RF25IRRNTZAXXLNPHEZZWMUCME/</a><br />\n漢光37號兵棋推演23日至30日進行8天7夜，是史上最長的一次兵推。這也是國防部首度將解放軍犯台時，國軍在台澎防衛作戰可「撐過一周」作為想定。國防部長邱國正今（19日）表示，國防部發現以往兵推時間匆忙，無法充分討論，因此決定延長兵推時間。<br />\n<br />\n立法院司法及法制上午與外交及國防委員會聯席審查，邀國防部就「國防部防衛後備動員署組織法」草案、《國防部組織法》及《國防部參謀本部組織法》修正草案報告並備詢，邱國正會前接受媒體聯訪時作了上述表示。<br />\n外界一直關切，共軍若犯台國軍到底能撐多久，國防部前部長馮世寬曾在立法院強調，國軍實力比以往大，「可撐不止兩周」。國防部前部長嚴德發也說過，國軍從來沒有撐多久的問題，心中只有一個信念，就是任何時候，絕對不讓敵人得逞。邱國正則說「打多久陪多久」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"3f538d93ff066c14d166f5570749a418f77e1227","tid":2499655,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf940eee165dba900c4da788893f9213e7795ef","tid":2499655,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"諗得太理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533eaf086a6bb780d7f1762f8c0cd0b0acc80d12","tid":2499655,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"